high_descs: Go to the counter on the right of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn left, go to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, cut the tomato on the upper shelf.
Stay at the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, put the knife on the lower shelf, close the refrigerator.
Stay at the refrigerator.
Take a slice of tomato from the refrigerator.
Turn around, go to the sink on the left.
Put the slice of tomato in the sink, turn the water on then off, take the tomato from the sink.
Turn left, go to the refrigerator.
Put the slice of tomato on the lower shelf of the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed slice of tomato in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Move across the kitchen to the drawer left of the sink.
Pick up the silver knife from the counter beside the sculpture.
Turn around, then move across the kitchen to the fridge.
Open the fridge, slice the tomato on the top shelf, close the fridge.
Go to the fridge then open the fridge
Put the knife on the bottom shelf, close the fridge.
Go to the fridge then open the fridge
Pick up the tomato slice from the tomato, close the fridge.
Turn around, then move across the kitchen to the sink.
Place tomato slice in the sink, fill sink with water, drain the sink and pick up the tomato slice.
Turn around, then move across the kitchen to the fridge.
Open the fridge, place tomato slice on the lower shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed tomato slice in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk forward to the stove then turn and face the corner.
Take the knife on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Open the door and slice the tomato on the shelf.
Close the door on the fridge.
Open the door and place the knife inside.
Close the door on the fridge.
Open the door to the fridge and take out a tomato slice, then close the door.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink, turn on the water, then remove the tomato.
Turn around, walk back to the fridge and open the door.
Place the tomato slice inside and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed tomato slice in the fridge.
